# Database Design Specification

**Project:** ECOS – Educational Content Operating System
**Version:** 1.0
**Database:** PostgreSQL 16+
**ORM:** Django ORM
**Migration Tool:** Django Migrations

---

# 1. Purpose

เอกสารนี้กำหนดโครงสร้างฐานข้อมูลของ ECOS ครอบคลุม

* Logical Data Model
* Entity Relationship Diagram (ERD)
* Physical Schema
* Naming Convention
* Index Strategy
* Constraints
* Migration Strategy
* Versioning
* Audit
* Backup & Recovery

---

# 2. Database Architecture

```text
                    PostgreSQL

            ┌────────────────────┐
            │ Identity           │
            │ Organization       │
            │ Curriculum         │
            │ Content            │
            │ Assessment         │
            │ AI Studio          │
            │ Marketplace        │
            │ Plugin             │
            │ Analytics          │
            │ Foundation         │
            └────────────────────┘
```

ใช้ **Single Database, Modular Schema** ในช่วง MVP และสามารถแยกฐานข้อมูลในอนาคตได้

---

# 3. Logical ERD

```text
Organization
    │
    ├── Users
    │
    ├── Courses
    │      │
    │      ├── Units
    │      │      │
    │      │      ├── Lessons
    │      │      │      │
    │      │      │      ├── Resources
    │      │      │      ├── Assessments
    │      │      │      └── AI Jobs
    │      │
    │      └── Competencies
    │
    ├── Templates
    ├── Plugins
    └── Workflow
```

---

